{"tid":372783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿信屋告急】母公司勁蝕5000萬 CEO年薪減兩萬！","createTime":"2017-08-24T14:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T16:26:49.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f27d3f77829ed2270009296a5e0475ba275c0cb","tid":372783,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"我都唔知佢而家做乜，賣嘉頓餅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503579498277&amp;issue=20170824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1503579498277%26issue%3D20170824&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1092c0f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503579498277&amp;issue=20170824</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n759阿信屋的母公司CEC國際（0759）於年報內指，2016/17年度之業績是創業38年來最差勁的業績，年報中顯示集團數名執行董事本年薪金比去年輕微減少。<br />\n<br />\n集團指，零售市道低迷，加上行業競爭激烈，以致收益錄得倒退。為減輕高成本和收益倒退的影響，759於各方面也作出成本控制。董事酬金方面，以行政總裁林偉駿來說，於今年4月底止年度，所獲薪金為127萬港元，比去年同期少約2萬。<br />\n<br />\n截至於本年4月底，經營中分店（不包括合作店）數目為243間，較去年同期淨減少28間。集團員工由去年2700名跌至今年2200名，數目隨分店數目流失，但平均每店前線人員數目仍然維持於4人。員工薪金方面，集團根據市場水平釐定，本年度薪資佔收益比重較去年上升0.3個百分點至9.2%。<br />\n<br />\nCEC國際上月底公布截至四月底止業績，全年虧損擴大至近5000萬元，其中阿信屋業務亦終於「見紅」蝕近3000萬元。"},{"pid":"c956398aea9866044f678047762724a3b097b6d9","tid":372783,"uid":93266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜"},{"pid":"77c19ca3571d2b97fd36edb29585ae9a93cb6fd9","tid":372783,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜</blockquote><br />\n越賣越支那味濃"},{"pid":"daf0271bc63c307ffe10adde1d1eee76ba863288","tid":372783,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜</blockquote><br />\n越賣越支那味濃</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿信屋算係咁 , 擺明車馬係做香港人生意<br />\n<br />\n唔似得優字頭果間野"},{"pid":"496d1d96d7370df097974b6b039f2e94957c8294","tid":372783,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜</blockquote><br />\n越賣越支那味濃</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿信屋算係咁 , 擺明車馬係做香港人生意<br />\n<br />\n唔似得優字頭果間野</blockquote><br />\n但而家入面d貨好似國貨公司咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfde62c1a0f987f8b20b1e6e0c7d90b915c41811","tid":372783,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜 , 越賣越雜</blockquote><br />\n越賣越支那味濃</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿信屋算係咁 , 擺明車馬係做香港人生意<br />\n<br />\n唔似得優字頭果間野</blockquote><br />\n但而家入面d貨好似國貨公司咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n競爭大左 , 貨源少左<br />\n<br />\n佢肯變已經算係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nin fact , 其實我好耐無幫趁"},{"pid":"2d1e7b86d5f24cb37b4506328913915eeee81ab1","tid":372783,"uid":293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"係果到買野<br />\n又係撚野超抵價  又乜乜折<br />\n之後一堆野又公價<br />\n<br />\n亂到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206d603e855935979383e6e07876e8d4248c24a7","tid":372783,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"689 折好型，大把高登連登仔幫襯<br />\n<br />\n點會執"},{"pid":"b604302e5480e08e98b856d11a0cf245714cecd8","tid":372783,"uid":55581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"我樓下間OK,個日本直送零食架仲多選擇過759<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eee11e0e42f6afbfbea1579cef3dbb392d10e86","tid":372783,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:56:40.000Z","msg":"減2萬<img 